object.customQuery:
select
	distinct insured.SystemId,
	insured.ParentId,
	insured.CMMContainer,
	insured.Id,
	insured.IndexName,
	insured.StatusCd,
	insured.EntityTypeCd,
	insured.PreferredDeliveryMethod,
	insured.TemporaryAddressOverrideInd,
	insured.NoEmailInd,
	insured.InspectionContact,
	insured.InspectionContactNumber,
	insured.InspectionContactPhoneType,
	insured.RowId,
	basicpolicy.PolicyNumber,
	basicpolicy.InceptionDt,
	BasicPolicy.PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion,
	addr.Addr1 as Addr1,
	addr.Addr2 as Addr2,
	addr.Addr3 as Addr3,
	addr.Addr4 as Addr4,
	addr.City as City,
	addr.StateProvCd as StateProvCd,
	addr.PostalCode as PostalCode
from
	insured
left join basicpolicy
on insured.SystemId = basicpolicy.SystemId 
and insured.CMMContainer = basicpolicy.CMMContainer 
left join addr 
on insured.SystemId = addr.SystemId 
and insured.CMMContainer = addr.CMMContainer 
and addr.AddrTypeCd = 'InsuredMailingAddr'
join advrxxchangedbeans 
on insured.SystemId = advrxxchangedbeans.SystemId 
and insured.CMMContainer = advrxxchangedbeans.CMMContainer 
and concat(adddt, addtm)>= '$$m_strtdt'
and concat(adddt, addtm) <= '$$m_Enddt'
where
	insured.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
